Retail Sales Analysis Dataset
This repository contains a set of cleaned CSV files used for analyzing retail business performance. The data covers customers, products, stores, and sales transactions.

Dataset Overview-

customers_cleaned.csv: Contains customer information such as names, gender, age, region, and signup dates.
products_cleaned.csv: Lists the items sold, including their category, brand, cost price, and selling price.
salesdata_cleaned.csv: This is the main file containing all transaction details, including quantities sold, discounts, revenue, and profit for every order.
stores_cleaned.csv: Provides details about the different store locations, their types (e.g., Flagship, Franchise), and their monthly operating costs.
returns_cleaned.csv: Tracks which orders were returned and the reason for the return (e.g., defective, wrong item).
